Kigali House Price Predictor

Project for software dev course – predicts house prices in Kigali to help make ABC platform fairer.

Files
house_price_notebook.ipynb → data + model training
api.py → FastAPI backend
app.py → Streamlit web app (nice UI)
kigali_house_model.pkl → saved model
requirements.txt → packages to install

How to run (for teacher)
1. pip install -r requirements.txt
2. Start MongoDB (if using DB part)
3. python -m uvicorn api:app --reload   → API on http://127.0.0.1:8000
4. streamlit run app.py                 → web app in browser

Test with Postman: POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/predict
